    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "It's not to do with this parameter. The PS Core implementation of `Test-Connection` writes a majority of its data to the host stream, and then submits a rather less useful object to the output stream. We have another issue on that somewhere, @iSazonov might know where. Too sleepy at the present to dig that one up.\r\n\r\nI've been looking at fixing it and am happy to work on it, but we need to come to some consensus on what exactly the inner workings of that fix need to be first. ðŸ™‚ ",
